Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.66,0:00:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏降临
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.48,0:00:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算黑暗吞噬一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.13,0:00:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,持续闪烁的星屑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像朝阳那般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:15.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此刻燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.74,0:01:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为认识了迷之小动物 波克塔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被卷入来历不明事件里的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.25,0:01:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜.因巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和自称保护者的高里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是为了拯救迷般的城市 塔夫拉希亚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却把罪名嫁祸于我 到底怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.64,0:02:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那个罪名居然只是因为我是莉娜.因巴斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:06.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有被可疑的刺客和贵族的老太婆盯上了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还有那个把传说中的魔兽扎那法唤醒的大骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.34,0:02:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受不了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.44,0:02:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了我莉娜.因巴斯的手里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手是传说的魔兽也好 别的也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.62,0:02:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是小菜一碟 轻松搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:20.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.99,0:02:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是迷题还是有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么那么 这之后会怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:27.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,New comer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.62,0:02:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的旅行开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.33,0:03:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.59,0:03:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样和魔法道具有关的魔导书已经齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 谢谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 阿梅莉亚 你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.57,0:03:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 明白什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:45.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:48.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然无法轻易找到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个欧泽鲁所说的壶的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.75,0:03:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请找出红法师雷藏的灵魂沉睡之壶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并将其打碎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红法师雷藏的灵魂沉睡之壶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.58,0:04:09.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红法师 雷藏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为传说的贤者 失明魔导士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以他充沛的魔力和丰富的知识拯救了很多人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有让感染疫病的塔夫拉希亚民众沉睡并封印起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的恩人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.43,0:04:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但事实是他执念于治愈自己的双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.57,0:04:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解开失明双眼的前提是唤醒魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.27,0:04:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己也被毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:02.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个雷藏的灵魂沉睡之壶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个世界上的某处
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:08.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 所以必须去寻找那个壶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了解开我的故乡塔夫拉希亚的封印
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.45,0:05:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.51,0:05:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果只是那些倒还好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迷题还有很多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欧泽鲁为什么要让我们打破雷藏的灵魂沉睡之壶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 那个欧泽鲁是何方神圣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和雷藏又有什么关联
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有另外一点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰洛士也牵扯进这个事件里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.38,0:05:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始以为他的目标是扎那法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果好像没什么关联
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.20,0:05:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.13,0:05:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直说“那个是秘密”的老兄吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是那种会盲目行动的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然那家伙行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就肯定有什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.97,0:06:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把扎那法扔在一边不管的重大理由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.90,0:06:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.06,0:06:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比扎那法还厉害的麻烦事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好就是那样哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:45.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带食物过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的身体如何了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.07,0:07:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 壶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.39,0:07:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赛伦魔导士协会的大图书馆里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像也没有什么线索
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.74,0:07:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底该去哪儿找呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起壶的话 能想到的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从肉体的束缚中脱离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把灵魂寄托在虚假的容器上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概只有把我们变成这样时使用的那个壶了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.25,0:07:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个大呆子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说干了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个壶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.89,0:07:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们寻找的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.70,0:07:52.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.31,0:07:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.50,0:07:59.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用过光之剑 智力真的会被吸走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不至于那样啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.02,0:08:04.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在表扬你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从刚才开始就没找到半户人家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个公爵领地是受扎那法波及最大的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.71,0:08:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 回到刚才的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.40,0:08:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个壶是一个可以转移人类灵魂的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.92,0:08:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏称那个壶为“冥王之壶”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥王是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:34.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个冥王菲布利佐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以转换人类的灵魂 倒是般配的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷藏一旦遇到对自己构成危胁的情况时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.17,0:08:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用那个壶把自己的灵魂转换掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此 是那样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.09,0:08:59.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 那个壶在哪里有卖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:00.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有卖的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.03,0:09:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先回到乔康达的城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把一个个可能有关联的地方挖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.67,0:09:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别废话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.29,0:09:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利索点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不擅长这样的体力劳动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.79,0:09:24.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方真的有那个壶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说过了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.75,0:09:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有一个个的找了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.56,0:09:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,波克塔的故乡塔夫拉希亚 因为封印 所以进不去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能从这里开始找了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.46,0:09:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灵王结魔弹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.32,0:10:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.52,0:10:06.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直连到地下研究室
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.96,0:10:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪克利斯曾经在这里呆过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.28,0:10:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来真是个相当高级的研究室呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.98,0:10:28.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为使用了从塔夫拉希亚偷出来的资料啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.26,0:10:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来也有把冥王之壶一起带出来的可能性了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.49,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.16,0:10:38.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产生高等合成兽 并作为触媒的场所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:42.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然明白杰路的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还是先找冥王之壶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.44,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.05,0:11:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到里面还有这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.64,0:11:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像藏着什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印了什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.33,0:11:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像听到什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.80,0:11:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.19,0:11:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是鬼 还是蛇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鬼在唱歌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.42,0:11:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:53.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这是很好听的歌声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮的玫瑰也有刺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:56.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.51,0:11:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你们这是什么反应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜 那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.54,0:12:03.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来歌声是从那传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.25,0:12:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是盔甲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这里是放盔甲的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了吗 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.11,0:12:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上来就赏你个暴风弹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.81,0:13:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来也许会有冥王之壶的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.49,0:13:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞧你都干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.65,0:13:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 好像身体条件反射般地动了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.62,0:13:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,条件反射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个里面好像是空的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:21.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的歌声确实是从这个盔甲里传出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.51,0:13:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应该是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.22,0:13:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.50,0:13:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.06,0:13:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实有打中的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你突然之间都干了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纳玛生气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.51,0:13:56.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓的活盔甲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用某种手段让生命浮现出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:07.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听从自己意识行动的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是某种手段吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.11,0:14:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥王之壶的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不和突然弄疼人家的人说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.15,0:14:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像生气了啊 莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说啊 可疑的盔甲在唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还“哦呵呵”地笑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都会用攻击魔法打上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.11,0:14:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.01,0:14:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我倒觉得挺可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻击你是我们不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.59,0:14:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以跟我们谈一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纳玛是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.89,0:14:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们才要问你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 纳玛是你的名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.67,0:14:58.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纳…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.10,0:15:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是 又好像不是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.10,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什么名字无所谓了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 你知道有关壶之类的事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.76,0:15:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.76,0:15:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么知道的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.05,0:15:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小纳玛在寻找宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.21,0:15:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时起 就失去了意识 醒来就在这里唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.48,0:15:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说为什么会在唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为一个人很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.03,0:15:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那样子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之 照你的话来看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.28,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本来不是活盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是普通的人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.19,0:15:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得好像在哪里听过的声音 不愿意想出来的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.97,0:15:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.49,0:15:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个纳玛的声音在哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不可能是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:04.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那个人认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.45,0:16:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 声音先不说 语气完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.42,0:16:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是声音吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音相像的人可有不少哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道认识那个纳玛的双亲或者兄弟之类
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.24,0:16:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双亲兄弟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种盔甲有双亲和兄弟的话 倒真想看看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.77,0:16:29.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来 有记忆障碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.95,0:16:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否被冥王之壶影响还不得而知
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪儿找到那个壶的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个地下道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人着急
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点想出来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.12,0:16:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这家伙总是条件反射 自动出手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像变样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.26,0:17:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然用拖鞋打小纳玛 胆子真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.64,0:17:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.90,0:17:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜 好不容易找到的线索
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的是啊 如果那个人下跪说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.45,0:17:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“我错了 不会对小纳玛出手和反抗了”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,低头贴着地面的话 告诉你们也不是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说…说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要的话我是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了找壶去四处乱逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.18,0:17:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时先委屈一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.71,0:17:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁会低下头 对这种水壶头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.77,0:17:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然说我是水壶头
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到这份上 小纳玛也不能继续沉默了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用力量也要让你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有趣啊 我才要用力量逼问出壶的所在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 前提是你真知道壶的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.10,0:17:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西当然记得
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之分胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:17:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到外面来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.44,0:18:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个便利的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:05.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 竟敢小瞧我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.79,0:18:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要道歉的话就趁现在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.33,0:18:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是 要说出壶的所在就趁现在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.25,0:18:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不阻止她们不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.50,0:18:18.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜变成那样 可是无法阻止的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么莉娜对那个纳玛那么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.04,0:18:25.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天知道 个性不合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.00,0:18:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两人都别受伤就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先上了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度根本不用躲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.14,0:18:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这种卑鄙的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.55,0:18:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次轮到我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.24,0:18:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒文也能用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度对我来说只是小菜一碟啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.95,0:19:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.48,0:19:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炎之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之矢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.85,0:19:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.46,0:19:16.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么慌张地四处逃窜 真适合你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:25.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 普通的咒文马上就能复活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:28.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从某种意义上来说 比扎那法还麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.76,0:19:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 乖乖投降如何
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.73,0:19:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出来的话 就连那个一起轰了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有冰冻灵魂的霸王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请赋予吾冻结之怒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那招的话我就先出手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷击破
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.57,0:19:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那招也没用哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次该我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.96,0:19:50.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王冰河烈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.57,0:19:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何啊 变成电磁铁的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,磁铁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.30,0:20:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受到雷电的一击 你金属性的身体变成磁铁了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那个阴险的身体反而害了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 把那个铁制的垃圾融掉 做成真正的水壶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.80,0:20:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比黄昏还要昏暗者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比血液还要鲜红者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.21,0:20:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在时间之流中出现
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.77,0:20:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以汝之伟名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.58,0:20:23.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾于此黑暗起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快离开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.48,0:20:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.06,0:20:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不知道轻重啊 那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.76,0:20:28.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就阻止她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.91,0:20:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻挡在吾等前方所有的愚蠢之物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合吾等之力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:38.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赐与其平等的毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.46,0:20:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要变水壶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙破斩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是干了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下线索就没了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.69,0:20:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 对人家做了什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.79,0:21:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是缠人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 还想打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.23,0:21:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壶的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.90,0:21:12.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随便乱说的话 真把你变成水壶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:21.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以别把人家变成水壶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.42,0:21:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在请稍微忍耐下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.19,0:21:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在习惯新的手臂之前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.02,0:21:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
